e features can also be found in the package.\r\n<h3>Is the sytem flexible? Yes.</h3>\r\nThe responsivity is optional. It can be turned On and Off and customizable to adapt to your site or CSS framework (e.g. Bootstrap). You can use System or any Google Web Fonts (650+).\r\n<h3>Can I use more than one table on my site? Yes.</h3>\r\nYou can use any number of tables on your site or even on one single page using shortcodes.\r\n\r\n<strong>Go. Just Create!.</strong>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\";s:17:\"short_description\";N;s:7:\"tagline\";N;s:9:\"thumbnail\";s:70:\"http://granthweb.com/granthweb.com/wp-content/uploads/thumbnail_-3.png\";s:3:\"url\";s:92:\"http://codecanyon.net/item/go-pricing-wordpress-responsive-pricing-tables/3725820?ref=Granth\";s:12:\"purchase_url\";s:92:\"http://codecanyon.net/item/go-pricing-wordpress-responsive-pricing-tables/3725820?ref=Granth\";s:8:\"core_min\";N;s:6:\"wp_min\";s:3:\"3.5\";s:6:\"wp_max\";s:3:\"4.7\";s:7:\"version\";s:5:\"3.3.5\";s:4:\"date\";s:10:\"12-12-2016\";s:3:\"log\";O:8:\"stdClass\":30:{s:5:\"3.3.5\";O:8:\"stdClass\":5:{s:7:\"version\";s:5:\"3.3.5\";s:3:\"log\";s:184:\"<ul>\r\n	<li>[FIX] WordPress 4.7 compatibility fix</li>\r\n	<li>[FIX] Minor backend and frontend fixes</li>\r\n	<li>[IMPROVEMENT] Added Saudi Georgian Lari (GEL) to currency list</li>\r\n</ul>\";s:11:\"description\";N;s:7:\"details\";N;s:4:\"date\";s:10:\"12-12-2016\";}s:5:\"3.3.4\";O:8:\"stdClass\":5:{s:7:\"version\";s:5:\"3.3.4\";s:3:\"log\";s:864:\"<ul>\r\n	<li>[FIX] Fix for not displaying tables when using Visual Composer frontend editor</li>\r\n	<li>[FIX] Long, non-breaking texts in body and footer area fix for frontend and admin area</li>\r\n	<li>[FIX] WP Query resetting issue bugfix in nested WP Queries</li>\r\n	<li>[FIX] Incorrect tooltip positioning bugfix in responsive views</li>\r\n	<li>[FIX] Fix for maximum width problem in Chrome</li>\r\n	<li>[FIX] Column width problem fix in Edge</li>\r\n	<li>[FIX] Fix for column gap issue in \"reformatted\" HTML code</li>